{"tid":198633,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]光榮偽三國志大戰 - 三國志Legion出左啦(2)","createTime":"2017-04-12T16:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T01:10:56.000Z","uid":7371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1137ec32b26e63efec9966f8738e857227a527f8","tid":198633,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"光榮抄Sega三國志大戰出左隻三國Legion<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQ3J8L3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQ3J8L3.jpg&h=7722bc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65CoF5z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65CoF5z.jpg&h=52bf9d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/011835_cbf16a9d28a7cdcf857b0b46ad724425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F011835_cbf16a9d28a7cdcf857b0b46ad724425.jpg&h=6916f207&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3em5Na.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3em5Na.jpg&h=fa73ee39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6T5441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6T5441.jpg&h=398367d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I2A5K_n0JxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DI2A5K_n0JxU&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=15bf4d77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I2A5K_n0JxU</a><br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gamecity.ne.jp/legion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamecity.ne.jp%2Flegion%2F&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3dbc4718\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gamecity.ne.jp/legion/</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲基本介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.qoo-app.com/86720/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.qoo-app.com%2F86720%2F&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5aa2e165\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.qoo-app.com/86720/</a><br />\n<br />\n期間限定關攻略，有SR劉備拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=26953&amp;page=&amp;snA=10&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D26953%26page%3D%26snA%3D10%26last%3D&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=513e4641\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=26953&amp;page=&amp;snA=10&amp;last=</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻game故事對電腦AI較悶<br />\n但玩完故事第2章後開放pvp<br />\n對真人玩家就好玩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左山寨Sega三國志大戰<br />\n新加左合流系統<br />\n例如可5卡合流 vs 5卡合流<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7anP71O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7anP71O.jpg&h=b2c5a6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但合流完死時係全部人同時死<br />\n所以係好賭博性既系統黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\npvp自動編配對手好亂黎<br />\n一時勁到屈死你<br />\n一時雞到好易贏<br />\n呢點絕對有待改善<br />\n<br />\n打pvp拎到既資源可以抽人用<br />\n好易抽到強化娘升人用<br />\n完成部份任務都有強化娘<br />\n抽到SR以下既人都不妨食黎升人<br />\n食同陣形人會加經多D<br />\n分4個陣形用4隻色代表<br />\n<br />\n暫時UR卡好難抽亦設定得過屈<br />\nSR卡唔難抽到<br />\nAn版出早過iOS版<br />\n所以後者玩家初期pvp絕對被屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢隻光榮山寨game<br />\n差極都至少比Sega隻三國志大戰劣質手遊好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲內基本教學圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/235926_45bd757d8b6996813a68b76e7b25ce55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F235926_45bd757d8b6996813a68b76e7b25ce55.jpg&h=58b00120&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cj2NNot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcj2NNot.jpg&h=c631de2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/235929_01e9e6a867d82be4d8275353712b1db2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F235929_01e9e6a867d82be4d8275353712b1db2.jpg&h=8ef57f01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/235931_9cac09ffa0f3d91c3d86d4bdaa142862.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F235931_9cac09ffa0f3d91c3d86d4bdaa142862.jpg&h=d37c358d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0fZ0U0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0fZ0U0.jpg&h=9d041a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/235956_20876cacf383749ad1abbb231f0f123d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F235956_20876cacf383749ad1abbb231f0f123d.jpg&h=1d98da5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/235958_2e3dc71da60a9fe63c626f175785d0ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F235958_2e3dc71da60a9fe63c626f175785d0ac.jpg&h=a2cfe7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/235959_e3e311f5de76c8fe0902f6193b387ae7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F235959_e3e311f5de76c8fe0902f6193b387ae7.jpg&h=2953b523&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/13/000000_641dcbdcd377462eadde5a9738a8a393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F000000_641dcbdcd377462eadde5a9738a8a393.jpg&h=993de8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YTR1F0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.