片，測試幾次方法失敗，最後終於成功了！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QKWW2TaVzZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQKWW2TaVzZk&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8b127d78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QKWW2TaVzZk</a>"},{"pid":"24a4d134cc2b3f64011ad59be52382ed1a80c29d","tid":198633,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"遲啲分享高順通關演義辦法"},{"pid":"b09cfada279cfd220ed2c03bacb0d1f96ca6a3c0","tid":198633,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68736475a1230168e26a103f743f91c675a4c590","tid":198633,"uid":49935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:53:48.000Z","msg":"偽三國志大戰天?好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5f22b433a10bf009ae94aef159879f38b49caf","tid":198633,"uid":34008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"其實關羽同司馬懿應該邊個做主將好啲"},{"pid":"09d736c92944c64fc2c5538b9d56ad7f3b75d314","tid":198633,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實關羽同司馬懿應該邊個做主將好啲</blockquote><br />\n關羽"},{"pid":"38c2b3d9d8f19e82cf2514c401e24ede2ab9f2f0","tid":198633,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實關羽同司馬懿應該邊個做主將好啲</blockquote><br />\n君主, 統率技能優先做主"},{"pid":"f04568572b1eb030867934943ab1c80b98b06a3d","tid":198633,"uid":29768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"抽到小喬 睇唔明個戰法效果"},{"pid":"30158b2ca67ae8234f6cd6c1420a2ca8fb112d16","tid":198633,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽到小喬 睇唔明個戰法效果</blockquote><br />\n副將就唔洗理戰法啦"},{"pid":"ccc8b8c765f261f0cabddab18e3516c94bdb0307","tid":198633,"uid":42